body_html: I believe Dataset.from_generator() does support yielding dictionaries (of NumPy arrays), as long as you specify a dictionary-based structure in the output_types argument. If this is not the case, please file a bug with a way to reproduce the problem!

body: I believe `Dataset.from_generator()` *does* support yielding dictionaries (of NumPy arrays), as long as you specify a dictionary-based structure in the `output_types` argument. If this is not the case, please file a bug with a way to reproduce the problem!
